{"tid":1216898,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係唔可以遊行，但真係唔係咁遊法","createTime":"2019-06-13T11:22:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T11:23:50.000Z","uid":122994,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"23727211d767ab0abcb5215d9b59b04cff3921a2","tid":1216898,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:22:18.000Z","msg":"好多人話連續遊行好勁，一定震撼世界，仲有D人好樂觀覺得會多過100萬。<br />\n<br />\n但我想講現實真係無咩可能，有50萬已經係好好既成績。一來宣傳時間太短；二來衝正父親節；三來義士好攰；四來有人會覺得遊行已經行過，無用；五來一鼓作氣，再而衰，三而竭<br />\n<br />\n呢D因素外界係唔會理，今次人數少左既話實質上就係示弱，比人口實；就算一樣都係民意無變。世界就係咁殘酷，就係無左膠咁溫柔<br />\n<br />\n所以就算遊行都要有一定程度既「升級」，咁先會有效果，例如：<br />\n<br />\n1. 全民赤腳行：意味住感受當日學生既痛<br />\n<br />\n2. 每到整數時份一跪：意味求政確放過學生<br />\n<br />\n諸如此類既有象徵性升級，又可以提高遊行難度既「升級」。咁一來人數少左係必須；二來媒體會繼續有興趣報；三來為衝既義士打氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d84bb1179d67d671b2f3aed58fa9c7bf3aebcd","tid":1216898,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:22:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7eb6ee949b0e20e4e160edee20f654945b734b78","tid":1216898,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:22:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b2ec36fc3a18d36513127e0aabb66e3a14a7c621","tid":1216898,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:23:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1e96d49ba59936856081a67a0ec9e6471ebde476","tid":1216898,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:23:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"45db31c42a060a2f1be1727585dd7847e407efef","tid":1216898,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:23:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a512e1cfba007c4359eadfb3f61aa7251a